description:
In this coding challenge, I take a closer look at the Quick, Draw! dataset and create a simple node API to "replay" drawings of rainbows and cats using p5.js. #quickdraw #dataset 

💻 Code: https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/122-quick-draw

Links discussed in this video:
🔗 Quick, Draw! The Data: https://quickdraw.withgoogle.com/data
🔗 sketch-rnn: https://magenta.tensorflow.org/sketch-rnn-demo
🎥 Doodle Classifier: https://youtu.be/pqY_Tn2SIVA
🎥 What is JSON?: https://youtu.be/_NFkzw6oFtQ
